  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 180C.",
    "Melt 50g butter over medium heat in a skillet.",
    "Whisk in 50g flour until a smooth paste forms.",
    "Gradually pour 500ml vegetable stock, stirring until thickened.",
    "Stir in 200ml milk until sauce is velvety.",
    "Add 2 tbsp mustard, 1 tsp salt, 1/2 tsp pepper, and 2 tbsp olive oil, mixing well.",
    "Fold in 200g semolina until evenly coated.",
    "Transfer mixture to a greased baking dish and bake for 30 minutes until golden.",
    "Let rest 5 minutes before serving."
